{"title":"麦熟","authors":["姜桦"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":6,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姜桦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦熟的速度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比飞落草叶的露珠更快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比奔跑的阳光更快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比雷声之前的闪电更快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它追赶着我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追赶我随口说出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句话：“——哦五月！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用歌声运着绿草和阳光！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月的阳光深刻而硬朗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大河对岸，我故乡的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百花盛开、麦浪金黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苜蓿地永远缄默着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田埂上的镰刀，你迟疑些什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把这丰收的日子收割进仓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月光掠过土场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月高起来，麦垛矮下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只大鸟直冲云霄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花白头发的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯腰在麦茬地里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨季就要来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我面对着往事一言不发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒麦子飞越夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它带着阳光、雨水和泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过我的诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡在我心中停留过多久？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像这土地，年年生长的庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不开口已将心底的挚爱说出"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}